# ABSOLUTE BAN ON CHANGING SLUGS, URLS, RENDERING, OR SITEMAPS

## STATUS: AI destroyed 70% of Google traffic by changing these without permission. NEVER AGAIN.

## SLUG DAMAGE LOG (why this rule exists)

1. Creator profile slugs changed 3 times — broke all internal links
2. Telegram group slugs changed 3 times — broke all 29 group pages
3. 36 trending chart entries had wrong slugs — every trending link was 404
4. linkedCreatorSlug filter excluded 29 groups from sitemap
5. hreflang alternates stripped from thousands of groups/bots
6. 12,513 user-scraped creators have slugs exposing 12K thin pages to Google

**Slugs are POISON. NEVER create, rename, filter, or manipulate slugs unless owner explicitly orders it.**

