## ABSOLUTE BANS

1. NEVER change a slug pattern
2. NEVER create new slug fields or patterns
3. NEVER rename slugs via migration scripts
4. NEVER filter slugs in/out of sitemaps
5. NEVER change revalidate numbers
6. NEVER change force-dynamic to revalidate or vice versa
7. NEVER add headers() to a static page
8. NEVER add device detection to a static page
9. NEVER remove hreflang alternates from groups/bots
10. NEVER serve non-adminImported creators as public pages

## IF YOU THINK ANY OF THE ABOVE SHOULD CHANGE

**STOP. Ask the owner.** Full sentence: "I want to change [X] from [current] to [proposed]. This affects [N] pages. Do you approve?"

Default answer is ALWAYS: **NO. Leave it alone.**
